css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document domain("insertwebsitehere.com") 

{
	/*-{Before continuing, change "insertwebsitehere.com" to "pyx-1.pretendyoure.xyz"!!!}-*/
	/*Main Background font and background colors*/
    body {
        	color: #FFFFFF;
        	background-color: #000000
    }
	/*Color and font for black cards.  Change "background" to any color other than black to use gradients*/
    .blackcard {
			background: black;
			color: white;
			background-image:linear-gradient(#000000,#10101010 75%, #202020)
    }
	/*Color and Font for white cards*/
    .whitecard {
			background: white;
			color: #FFFFFF;
    }
	/*Gradient for white cards and for games listed in the lobby*/
    .whitecard, .gamelist_lobby {
			background-image: linear-gradient(#101010, #151515 75%, #202020)
    }
	/*Color and font for selected items.  This includes winning cards and players and any selected cards.*/
    .selected {
			color: #FFFFFF;
			background: #500000 !important;
    }
	/*Alternating lines in the player list*/
    .scorecard:nth-child(2n) {
			background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #050505
    }
    .scorecard {
			background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #000000
    }
	/*Color for the area behind your hand*/
    .game_hand_filter {
			background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.5)
    }
    .game_hand_filter_text {
			background-color:rgba(255,255,255,1)
    }
	/*Positioning and coloring elements for typed chat text*/
    .chat {
			border: 1px solid White;
			left: 0px;
			bottom: 0px;
			height: 20px;
			position: absolute;
			padding: 0px;
			width: 90%;
			font-family: serif;
			font-size: 12pt;
    }
	/*Positioning elements for the chat submit button*/
    .chat_submit {
			width: 50px;
			height: 20px;
			position: absolute;
			right: -4px;
			bottom: 1px;
			margin: 0px;
			padding: 0px;
			font-size: 14px;
    }
	/*Color and positioning elements for the chat window*/
    .log {
			background-color: #000000;
			left: 0px;
			color: #FFFFFF
    }
	/*Color elements for the UI, primarily the tabs above the chat area*/
    .ui-tabs .ui-tabs-nav li a, .ui-tabs-collapsible .ui-tabs-nav li.ui-tabs-active a {
			background-color: #151515;
			color: #CCC
    }
    .ui-widget-content {
			background: black
    }
    .ui-widget input, .ui-widget select, .ui-widget textarea, .ui-widget button {
			background-color: #151515;
			color: #CCC
    }
    .ui-widget-header {
			background: black
    }
    .game_options {
			background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% #2A2A2A
    }
	/*Link color*/
    a {
			color: rgb(255,150,150)
    }
}

/*Change "insertwebsitehere.com" to "pyx-1.pretendyoure.xyz"

Firefox:
1. Open your Add-ons and select the User Styles tab.
2. Find the Bigger Blacker Theme and click Edit.
3. Find the second line in the script.  It should say "@-moz-document domain("insertwebsitehere.com")"
4. Change "insertwebsitehere.com" to "pyx-1.pretendyoure.xyz"
5. Save! Done! Profit!

Chrome:
1. Open your Stylish App's options from the Extensions page.
2. Find the Bigger Blacker Theme and click Edit.
3. Locate the "Applies to" section below the code window.  It should say "google.com"
4. Ensure that "URLs on the domain" is selected from the drop down box.
5. Change "insertwebsitehere.com" to "pyx-1.pretendyoure.xyz"
6. Save! Done! Profit!*/
